IGNOU Assignment Marks Fetcher
Description

A Python automation tool that retrieves IGNOU BCA assignment marks for multiple students using enrollment numbers from a text file. The script displays real-time progress in the command line, sorts students based on total assignment marks, and generates a structured text report.

Features
Reads multiple enrollment numbers from a text file.
Fetches assignment marks from the IGNOU Grade Card portal.
Displays results in real time in the command line.
Calculates total assignment marks automatically.
Sorts students by total marks.
Generates a formatted text report (gradecard_results.txt).
Technologies Used
Python
Requests
BeautifulSoup4
Requirements
Python 3.9 or later
requests
beautifulsoup4

Install dependencies:

pip install requests beautifulsoup4
How to Run
Add enrollment numbers to student_list.txt (one per line).
Run:
python main.py
The script will:
Retrieve assignment marks.
Display live results in the terminal.
Generate gradecard_results.txt.
Output
Live command-line result display.
Formatted text report containing assignment marks and total scores.
